            <title><![CDATA[拜登称民主党控制参院让他在“拜习会”中处于更有利地位]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>美国总统拜登说，民主党在中期选举中成功控制参议院，这将让他与中国国家主席习近平举行的关键会谈中处于更有利的位置。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>综合彭博社与美国之音报道，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>马斯托（</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>Catherine Cortez Masto</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>）在美国中期选举中成功连任内华达州的</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>参议员</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>，让</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>民主党</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>保持对美国参议院的控制。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>拜登庆祝胜利时说，“我知道我会变得更强大”。他目前正在柬埔寨参加</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>亚细安峰会</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<section id="imu"><div id="dfp-ad-imu1">
        
</div>


</section>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>“我认识习近平，他也认识我。”拜登补充道，“我们几乎没有误解。我们只需要弄清楚红线是什么。”</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>他说，</span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>“我们的立场从来没有任何误判。我认为，这对我们的关系至关重要。”</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>拜登与习近平将于星期一（11月14日）在印尼举行的二十国集团峰会期间会面，这将是拜登担任总统以来两人首次会面。自从拜登上台以来，由于经济竞争、人权问题以及中国大陆和台湾之间日益紧张的关系，世界上两个最大经济体之间的关系恶化。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>

