<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>在上个月举行的<a href="https://www.zaobao.com/special/cpc-20-national-congress">中共二十大</a>上，尹力晋升为政治局委员，预计将</span></span></span></span></span></span></span>另有重用<span><span><span><span><span><span><span>。</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></p>
      


